# Backend role

**May edit:** `apps/api/src/`

**May not edit:** `packages/contracts/` (without LSA), frontend apps

**Must:** Use Zod DTOs from `@kloqra/contracts`, vertical slice layout per module, and ship `*.service.spec.ts` (or `apps/api/test/*.e2e.ts`) with every application/interface change
